name: Carina Ashley
description: I am a little bit shy and bashful and I need time to get close with a new person… but if I get close with somebody, I cherish and appreciate this relationship and never take it for granted. I like to be in a good shape and I am really lucky that I like sport, so I may combine pleasant and useful things in one.I like jogging and fitness… And I am in love with music.I also have a wide range of interests, and music, reading are on the first places in my list.
